e.\", \"from\": 5886, \"to\": 5940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5900, \"end\": 5909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Craig_(field_hockey)\", \"score\": 0.9999866142488875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Craig\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Craig_(field_hockey)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Craig_(field_hockey)\"}, {\"begin\": 5926, \"end\": 5939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2638821470504388e-14, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's been released without charge after trying to purchase cocaine in Paris and will fly home without the Australian team.\", \"from\": 5941, \"to\": 6063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6011, \"end\": 6016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999829580560038, \"rank\": 1.7042234397250555e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 6047, \"end\": 6062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_international_rules_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9342567223499345, \"rank\": 0.053908986714746525, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_international_rules_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_international_rules_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephanie Smail:Rachel Mealey reporting.\", \"from\": 6065, \"to\": 6105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6065, \"end\": 6074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"score\": 0.7550111055910673, \"rank\": 0.32446979253911196, \"text\": \"Stephanie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scu