"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\"}, {\"begin\": 6271, \"end\": 6277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999998863, \"rank\": 1.4617526332621485e-13, \"text\": \"Qantas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Qantas says his pay will be docked because of the airline's high court loss and the recent settlement over flight cancellations.\", \"from\": 6329, \"to\": 6457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6329, \"end\": 6335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999998863, \"rank\": 1.4617526332621485e-13, \"text\": \"Qantas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our business reporter David Taylor joined me earlier.\", \"from\": 6458, \"to\": 6511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"David, why has Alan Joyce's payout been slashed by so much?\", \"from\": 6512, \"to\": 6571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6527, \"end\": 6537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Joyce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9388257792739947e-15, \"text\": \"Alan Joyce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13414980\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Joyce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Joyce\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"David Taylor:Steph, this is essentially the outcome of a performance review by management.\", \"from\": 6573, \"to\": 6663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Qantas has released the results publicly today via the Stock Exchange.\", \"from\": 6664, \"to\": 6734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6664, \"end\": 6670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9957127849594194e-18, \"text\": \"Qantas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement shared to the ASX, Qantas confirmed Mr Joyce's executive pay would be slashed after the airline lost its high court battle over the illegal sacking of ground staff in 2020 and a recent settlement with the ACCC over flight cancellations.\", \"from\": 6735, \"to\": 6986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6764, \"end\": 6767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Securities_Exchange\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.866198346676613e-23, \"text\": \"ASX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Securities_Exchange\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Securities_Exchange\"}, {\"begin\": 6769, \"end\": 6775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9957127849594194e-18, \"text\": \"Qantas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\"}, {\"begin\": 6789, \"end\": 6794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\", \"score\": 0.9999963884046527, \"rank\": 3.6115669576005673e-06, \"text\": \"Joyce\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\"}, {\"begin\": 6955, \"end\": 6959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Competition_and_Consumer_Commission_v_Baxter_Healthcare_Pty_Ltd\", \"score\": 0.999996134319272, \"rank\": 3.865644045910936e-06, \"text\": \"ACCC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Competition_and_Consumer_Commission_v_Baxter_Healthcare_Pty_Ltd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Competition_and_Consumer_Commission_v_Baxter_Healthcare_Pty_Ltd\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Qantas admitted to misleading customers and, subject to federal court approval, will pay a $100 million penalty.\", \"from\": 6987, \"to\": 7099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6987, \"end\": 6993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9957127849594194e-18, \"text\": \"Qantas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The events, the board said, damaged Qantas and its reputation and caused considerable harm to relationships with customers, employees and other stakeholders.\", \"from\": 7100, \"to\": 7257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7136, \"end\": 7142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9957127849594194e-18, \"text\": \"Qantas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Interestingly, Steph, the board said there were no findings of deliberate wrongdoing by management, but rather mistakes.\", \"from\": 7258, \"to\": 7378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephanie Smail:And what message is Qantas trying to send with this pay cut?\", \"from\": 7380, \"to\": 7456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7380, \"end\": 7389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Plum\", \"score\": 0.7428375225750884, \"rank\": 0.3461858850257596, \"text\": \"Stephanie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Plum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Plum\"}, {\"begin\": 7390, \"end\": 7395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"score\": 0.9999992977382327, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Smail\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\"}, {\"begin\": 7416, \"end\": 7422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9957127849594194e-18, \"text\": \"Qantas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"David Taylor:The message is quite simple.\", \"from\": 7458, \"to\": 7499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you make a decision that is not in the interests of the company's stakeholders, and specifically shareholders that give the company money to invest and expand and perform for all stakeholders, you will be financially punished.\", \"from\": 7500, \"to\": 7729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The question is, is this amount specifically enough to do that?\", \"from\": 7730, \"to\": 7793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, analysts say it is a responsible decision by the board.\", \"from\": 7794, \"to\": 7855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's fund manager Roger Montgomery.\", \"from\": 7856, \"to\": 7893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7876, \"end\": 7892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_de_Montgomery\", \"score\": 0.999995665456212, \"rank\": 4.3345623920301145e-06, \"text\": \"Roger Montgomery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_de_Montgomery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_de_Montgomery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roger Montgomery:I think the board has done the right thing considering the airline lost its high court battle over what's now being described as an illegal sacking of ground staffback in 2020.\", \"from\": 7895, \"to\": 8088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So that alone is enough for the review of a salary of any CEO of a company that has been found to act in a way that's inconsistent with a company that wants to maintain its brand reputation.\", \"from\": 8089, \"to\": 8279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"David Taylor:Just on that though, it's clear that that was ruled illegal and yet the ASX announcement says there was no findings of deliberate wrongdoing by management.\", \"from\": 8281, \"to\": 8449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8366, \"end\": 8369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Securities_Exchange\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.134622057615845e-16, \"text\": \"ASX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Securities_Exchange\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Securities_Exchange\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How does that add up?\", \"from\": 8450, \"to\": 8471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roger Montgomery:Good question.\", \"from\": 8473, \"to\": 8504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8473, \"end\": 8489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_de_Montgomery\", \"score\": 0.999995665456212, \"rank\": 4.3345623920301145e-06, \"text\": \"Roger Montgomery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_de_Montgomery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_de_Montgomery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's a question to ask the company.\", \"from\": 8505, \"to\": 8550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not make sense and it's certainly a question for the company to answer.\", \"from\": 8551, \"to\": 8630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephanie Smail:Fund manager Roger Montgomery there.\", \"from\": 8632, \"to\": 8684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8632, \"end\": 8641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_McMahon\", \"score\": 0.7119810765213895, \"rank\": 0.32381375770021853, \"text\": \"Stephanie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_McMahon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_McMahon\"}, {\"begin\": 8642, \"end\": 8647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"score\": 0.9999992977382327, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Smail\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\"}, {\"begin\": 8661, \"end\": 8677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_de_Montgomery\", \"score\": 0.999995665456212, \"rank\": 4.3345623920301145e-06, \"text\": \"Roger Montgomery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_de_Montgomery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_de_Montgomery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And David, Australia's biggest companies are about to reveal how profitable they have been over the past 12 months.\", \"from\": 8685, \"to\": 8800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8696, \"end\": 8705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9273186763601371, \"rank\": 0.04126347937654592, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AMP has reported this morning.\", \"from\": 8801, \"to\": 8831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8801, \"end\": 8804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMP_Limited\", \"score\": 0.9999864350485589, \"rank\": 7.881681742644504e-06, \"text\": \"AMP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMP_Limited\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMP_Limited\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What did it have to say?\", \"from\": 8832, \"to\": 8856, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"David Taylor:Well, better news for shareholders because it's had a rocky few years.\", \"from\": 8858, \"to\": 8941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"AMP shares have rocketed up after a solid earnings result.\", \"from\": 8942, \"to\": 9000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8942, \"end\": 8945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMP_Limited\", \"score\": 0.9999996461573972, \"rank\": 3.456503872959854e-07, \"text\": \"AMP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMP_Limited\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMP_Limited\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Profit after tax rose 5.4% to $118 million.\", \"from\": 9001, \"to\": 9044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Steph, as for upcoming results, global investment make UBS expects corporate Australian earnings to be a fraction lower this time around.\", \"from\": 9045, \"to\": 9186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9104, \"end\": 9107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UBS\", \"score\": 0.9999985562358424, \"rank\": 1.4437661579310523e-06, \"text\": \"UBS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UBS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UBS\"}, {\"begin\": 9126, \"end\": 9136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.8661149056147626, \"rank\": 0.1328221947569258, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's predicting earnings from ASX listed companies on average will have fallen 3.5% in the past financial year.\", \"from\": 9187, \"to\": 9298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9217, \"end\": 9220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Securities_Exchange\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.374137509324222e-22, \"text\": \"ASX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Securities_Exchange\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Securities_Exchange\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, that's 2023 to 2024, following a 2.9% drop in the previous year.\", \"from\": 9299, \"to\": 9374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephanie Smail:David Taylor there.\", \"from\": 9376, \"to\": 9411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9376, \"end\": 9385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"score\": 0.9999619995594556, \"rank\": 3.445860038465541e-05, \"text\": \"Stephanie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\"}, {\"begin\": 9386, \"end\": 9391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"score\": 0.9999992977382327, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Smail\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Childcare workers have welcomed a significant pay increase, saying it will help address the staff shortages that have been plaguing the sector.\", \"from\": 9412, \"to\": 9555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The federal government has announced a 15% wage increase to be rolled out over 12 months from this December.\", \"from\": 9556, \"to\": 9664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advocates say the bump in pay is also a major step forward for gender equity, as Kathleen Ferguson reports.\", \"from\": 9665, \"to\": 9772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9746, \"end\": 9763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999988506444663, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kathleen Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anthony Albanese:What do you think about my drawing, Ned?\", \"from\": 9774, \"to\": 9831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9774, \"end\": 9790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}, {\"begin\": 9827, \"end\": 9830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ned_Flanders\", \"score\": 0.891922360079569, \"rank\": 0.1203523065080002, \"text\": \"Ned\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ned_Flanders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ned_Flanders\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you think it's good?\", \"from\": 9832, \"to\": 9855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:The Prime Minister, Anthony Albanese, has a crack at some of the crafts which help nurture the country's young.\", \"from\": 9857, \"to\": 9986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9857, \"end\": 9874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999988506444663, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kathleen Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\"}, {\"begin\": 9895, \"end\": 9911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anthony Albanese:Hey, what do you reckon?\", \"from\": 9988, \"to\": 10029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Opinion:That looks weird.\", \"from\": 10031, \"to\": 10056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can I have a look?\", \"from\": 10057, \"to\": 10075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can I have a look, Tom?\", \"from\": 10076, \"to\": 10099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:He visited the Sydney Early Childcare Centre after announcing a 15% pay increase for the sector's workers.\", \"from\": 10101, \"to\": 10225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10134, \"end\": 10140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9998970750587085, \"rank\": 5.854989984302666e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anthony Albanese:They deserve more than our thanks.\", \"from\": 10227, \"to\": 10278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They deserve decent wages and conditions.\", \"from\": 10279, \"to\": 10320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:Under the deal, workers will get 10% by this Christmas and a further 5% by December next year.\", \"from\": 10322, \"to\": 10434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10322, \"end\": 10339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999988506444663, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kathleen Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It equates to around an extra $100 a week and will cost $3.6 billion.\", \"from\": 10435, \"to\": 10504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Karen Moran is a long-time educator.\", \"from\": 10505, \"to\": 10541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10505, \"end\": 10510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_people\", \"score\": 0.960687598517153, \"rank\": 0.029313774367332474, \"text\": \"Karen\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Karen Moran:This decision today will change people's lives.\", \"from\": 10543, \"to\": 10602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It means that early childhood educators who have been relying on Food Bank to feed their own families will not have to do that anymore.\", \"from\": 10603, \"to\": 10738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And those that work two and three jobs just to make ends meet will be able to spend more time with their families.\", \"from\": 10739, \"to\": 10853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:But the deal is conditional.\", \"from\": 10855, \"to\": 10901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10855, \"end\": 10872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999988506444663, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kathleen Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In order to receive the pay bump, childcare centres will have to limit their fee increases to 4.4% during the next 12 months.\", \"from\": 10902, \"to\": 11027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Minister for Early Childcare, Education and Youth, Dr Anne Aly, says the sector's role in society is critical.\", \"from\": 11028, \"to\": 11142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11086, \"end\": 11094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Aly\", \"score\": 0.9999999999789679, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Aly\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Aly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Aly\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Anne Aly:We know that brain development is... 90% of brain development occurs in those first five years.\", \"from\": 11144, \"to\": 11251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not babysitting, this is not wiping bums and noses.\", \"from\": 11252, \"to\": 11311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is education.\", \"from\": 11312, \"to\": 11330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We see you, we hear you, we acknowledge you.\", \"from\": 11331, \"to\": 11375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know the vital and professional work that you do.\", \"from\": 11376, \"to\": 11428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:The early childcare sector says it's been a long and hard-fought battle.\", \"from\": 11430, \"to\": 11520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Georgie Dent is the CEO of advocacy group The Parenthood.\", \"from\": 11521, \"to\": 11578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11529, \"end\": 11533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._M._Dent\", \"score\": 0.9961429057188166, \"rank\": 0.003872029027129565, \"text\": \"Dent\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._M._Dent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._M._Dent\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Georgie Dent:This is a long overdue recognition of the incredible contribution that early childhood educators make to our children, to our communities, to families.\", \"from\": 11580, \"to\": 11744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is such a fantastic achievement.\", \"from\": 11745, \"to\": 11780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:Georgie Dent says this pay increase is desperately needed to combat a worker shortage in the sector, which is mostly made up of women.\", \"from\": 11782, \"to\": 11934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11782, \"end\": 11799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999988506444663, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kathleen Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\"}, {\"begin\": 11808, \"end\": 11812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._M._Dent\", \"score\": 0.9961429057188166, \"rank\": 0.003872029027129565, \"text\": \"Dent\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._M._Dent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._M._Dent\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Georgie Dent:The sector is overjoyed.\", \"from\": 11936, \"to\": 11973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This has been a long-realised dream.\", \"from\": 11974, \"to\": 12010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have known that early childhood educators have been chronically underpaid and undervalued.\", \"from\": 12011, \"to\": 12104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have seen in recent years the accelerating exit of early educators from the sector, which has put incredible pressure on services.\", \"from\": 12105, \"to\": 12238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:This is an interim measure which will be in place for two years while the federal government reviews the sector.\", \"from\": 12240, \"to\": 12370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The federal education minister, Jason Clare, says it will be up to childcare centres and providers to sign on to the scheme.\", \"from\": 12371, \"to\": 12495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12403, \"end\": 12414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Clare\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jason Clare\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Clare\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Clare\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he says if centres do not sign up, they should be prepared to lose staff to competitors.\", \"from\": 12496, \"to\": 12588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jason Clare:This is a cost-of-living win-win.\", \"from\": 12590, \"to\": 12635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's good for workers and it's good for parents.\", \"from\": 12636, \"to\": 12684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And at its heart, this is good for education, for the next generation, setting our kids up for success.\", \"from\": 12685, \"to\": 12788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:Shadow Treasurer Angus Taylor supports higher wages but says bringing down inflation is the best way to increase pay.\", \"from\": 12790, \"to\": 12925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12790, \"end\": 12807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999988506444663, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kathleen Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\"}, {\"begin\": 12825, \"end\": 12837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angus_Taylor_(politician)\", \"score\": 0.9999998057673072, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angus Taylor\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angus_Taylor_(politician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angus_Taylor_(politician)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Angus Taylor:Well, we want to see higher real wages, which means lower prices for everything, for all Australians, PK.\", \"from\": 12927, \"to\": 13045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12927, \"end\": 12939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angus_Taylor_(politician)\", \"score\": 0.9999998057673072, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angus Taylor\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angus_Taylor_(politician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angus_Taylor_(politician)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we will look at the detail of this proposal that Labor's putting forward.\", \"from\": 13046, \"to\": 13123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13099, \"end\": 13104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999989842236275, \"rank\": 1.0157773592762755e-06, \"text\": \"Labor\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If it can raise real wages for Australians, of course we are going to support it.\", \"from\": 13124, \"to\": 13205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's our position.\", \"from\": 13206, \"to\": 13226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:The United Workers Union says the increase sends a strong message to women.\", \"from\": 13228, \"to\": 13321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13265, \"end\": 13270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998702094532157, \"rank\": 0.00010168496381491603, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jo Schofield is the union's national president.\", \"from\": 13322, \"to\": 13369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13322, \"end\": 13324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jo_Grant\", \"score\": 0.9889016153020836, \"rank\": 0.011217347220981473, \"text\": \"Jo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jo_Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jo_Grant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jo Schofield:Just this week, we did a survey that showed 60% of educators wanted to leave within three years.\", \"from\": 13371, \"to\": 13480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13371, \"end\": 13373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jo_Grant\", \"score\": 0.9889016153020836, \"rank\": 0.011217347220981473, \"text\": \"Jo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jo_Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jo_Grant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"97% of centres have seen educators walk out in the last year, and the single factor in that is the low pay.\", \"from\": 13481, \"to\": 13588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kathleen Ferguson:She says while the union will continue advocating for better pay and conditions, this is a good start.\", \"from\": 13590, \"to\": 13710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephanie Smail:Kathleen Ferguson reporting.\", \"from\": 13712, \"to\": 13756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13712, \"end\": 13721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"score\": 0.5492954330549386, \"rank\": 0.7574516253394934, \"text\": \"Stephanie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\"}, {\"begin\": 13722, \"end\": 13727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"score\": 0.9999992977382327, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Smail\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\"}, {\"begin\": 13728, \"end\": 13745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"score\": 0.9999988506444663, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kathleen Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathleen_Ferguson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On ABC Radio across Australia, streaming online, and on the ABC Listen app this is The World Today, thanks for your company.\", \"from\": 13757, \"to\": 13881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13760, \"end\": 13769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999853328238423, \"rank\": 1.1351872386948757e-05, \"text\": \"ABC Radio\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 13777, \"end\": 13786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9775862137681938, \"rank\": 0.022700287901061607, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 13817, \"end\": 13831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_ABC_Radio_(Australia)\", \"score\": 0.9999999998676685, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ABC Listen app\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_ABC_Radio_(Australia)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_ABC_Radio_(Australia)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thousands of people have streamed onto the streets in cities across the United Kingdom to share messages of peace amid ongoing race riots.\", \"from\": 13882, \"to\": 14020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13954, \"end\": 13968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999416652168408, \"rank\": 5.1187504958855637e-05, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Counter-protesters are taking a stand as police battle widespread violence targeting Muslims and immigrants.\", \"from\": 14021, \"to\": 14129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14106, \"end\": 14113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.8219235626117122, \"rank\": 0.19097275528360222, \"text\": \"Muslims\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The unrest has been triggered by false information about the fatal stabbing of three children in the town of Southport.\", \"from\": 14130, \"to\": 14249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14239, \"end\": 14248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport\", \"score\": 0.929084069483205, \"rank\": 0.0692170259443945, \"text\": \"Southport\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexandra Humphries reports.\", \"from\": 14250, \"to\": 14278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14250, \"end\": 14259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9741241987809238, \"rank\": 0.01714576156288012, \"text\": \"Alexandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexandra Humphries:After a week of chaos, Britons are taking a stand.\", \"from\": 14280, \"to\": 14350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14323, \"end\": 14330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_people\", \"score\": 0.8870153850174239, \"rank\": 0.10077110758004391, \"text\": \"Britons\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thousands taking to the streets to protest the anti-immigrant unrest that swept the nation.\", \"from\": 14351, \"to\": 14442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many here in London are holding signs with phrases like refugees welcome and no room for Nazis.\", \"from\": 14443, \"to\": 14538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14456, \"end\": 14462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9977892406584271, \"rank\": 0.002128563817761436, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are  Opinion:We are not going to let fascists, we are not going to let racists and the far right march here.\", \"from\": 14539, \"to\": 14650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Opinion:My parents' generation went through great sacrifices to fight against fascism from Germany and it started off with small groups on the streets attacking immigrants or in those days Jews.\", \"from\": 14652, \"to\": 14846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14743, \"end\": 14750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9998713557789631, \"rank\": 7.700391000500377e-05, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 14841, \"end\": 14845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_Jews_in_Germany\", \"score\": 0.8792287682170313, \"rank\": 0.06919131104584467, \"text\": \"Jews\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_Jews_in_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_Jews_in_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now the same types of people are on the streets in this country.\", \"from\": 14847, \"to\": 14911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's absolutely disgraceful and I am standing here against that.\", \"from\": 14912, \"to\": 14976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexandra Humphries:Far right groups were reportedly planning to target asylum centres and immigration lawyers across Britain overnight.\", \"from\": 14978, \"to\": 15114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15096, \"end\": 15103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9774010901765449, \"rank\": 0.012943446639213391, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Businesses have closed early, shopkeepers have also boarded up their premises.\", \"from\": 15115, \"to\": 15193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For these workers in the northern English town of Oldham, there is real concern.\", \"from\": 15194, \"to\": 15274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15244, \"end\": 15250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oldham\", \"score\": 0.9998613956398028, \"rank\": 0.00013019926401843958, \"text\": \"Oldham\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oldham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oldham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Opinion:People are scared, yeah.\", \"from\": 15276, \"to\": 15308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of customers coming in, looking over their shoulder.\", \"from\": 15309, \"to\": 15367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of people walking past looking over their shoulders.\", \"from\": 15368, \"to\": 15426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can see they are frightened, yeah.\", \"from\": 15427, \"to\": 15465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Opinion:We are upholsterers, we work down here in the mill down here.\", \"from\": 15467, \"to\": 15536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like I say, everyone's evacuated and that.\", \"from\": 15537, \"to\": 15579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Opinion:I do not want to say it but we are shut down so we are not earning nothing.\", \"from\": 15581, \"to\": 15664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexandra Humphries:Some 6,000 specialist officers have been deployed to curb the unrest.\", \"from\": 15666, \"to\": 15755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15666, \"end\": 15675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9829119299246594, \"rank\": 0.016367445753284367, \"text\": \"Alexandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"London Metropolitan Police Commissioner Mark Rowley described the mobilisation as a standing army.\", \"from\": 15756, \"to\": 15854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15763, \"end\": 15782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_Police\", \"score\": 0.9999997698892267, \"rank\": 1.8619299488818407e-07, \"text\": \"Metropolitan Police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_Police\"}, {\"begin\": 15796, \"end\": 15807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Rowley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.510793545810169e-15, \"text\": \"Mark Rowley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Rowley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Rowley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark Rowley:We have changed our tactics in the last couple of days.\", \"from\": 15856, \"to\": 15923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So besides marshalling more officers, we are brigading some of them at key strategic locations across the country to give us more agility to respond to wherever the protests are most intense.\", \"from\": 15924, \"to\": 16115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexandra Humphries:It's been the worst outbreak of violence in Britain in more than a decade, sparked by false information spread after the stabbing deaths of three young girls at a dance class in Southport.\", \"from\": 16117, \"to\": 16325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16117, \"end\": 16126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9829119299246594, \"rank\": 0.016367445753284367, \"text\": \"Alexandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\"}, {\"begin\": 16181, \"end\": 16188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9789883143642801, \"rank\": 0.015792010228253193, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 16315, \"end\": 16324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport\", \"score\": 0.9777871844893905, \"rank\": 0.021791727481846806, \"text\": \"Southport\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Deputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner is reassuring the public that the situation can be controlled.\", \"from\": 16326, \"to\": 16435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16359, \"end\": 16372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Rayner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Rayner\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Rayner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Rayner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Angela Rayner:What has been heartening is to see the community response.\", \"from\": 16437, \"to\": 16509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16437, \"end\": 16450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Rayner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Rayner\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Rayner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Rayner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vast majority of the British people see this for what it is, that it is criminality, it is thuggish behaviour.\", \"from\": 16510, \"to\": 16624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16535, \"end\": 16549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_people\", \"score\": 0.6374133129737312, \"rank\": 0.5688407813993288, \"text\": \"British people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not a legitimate complaint to throw bricks at police and to try and set fire to public buildings.\", \"from\": 16625, \"to\": 16728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lord Michael Howard:We are witnessing lawless disorder which can not be tolerated, which must be met with the full force of the law and is being met with the full force of the law.\", \"from\": 16730, \"to\": 16910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexandra Humphries:Lord Michael Howard is a former Home Secretary of the United Kingdom.\", \"from\": 16912, \"to\": 17001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16912, \"end\": 16921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9723915235394918, \"rank\": 0.01647448102077623, \"text\": \"Alexandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\"}, {\"begin\": 16937, \"end\": 16951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Howard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5605327193840213e-21, \"text\": \"Michael Howard\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Howard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Howard\"}, {\"begin\": 16964, \"end\": 16978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Home_Secretary\", \"score\": 0.9999999992870698, \"rank\": 5.133335182447748e-10, \"text\": \"Home Secretary\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Home_Secretary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Home_Secretary\"}, {\"begin\": 16986, \"end\": 17000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9967979744574662, \"rank\": 0.00209811981131417, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lord Michael Howard:There is undoubtedly a lot of pent-up frustration at various things, including particularly the level of immigration.\", \"from\": 17003, \"to\": 17140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have had unprecedented levels of immigration in recent years and that is something that people are frustrated about.\", \"from\": 17141, \"to\": 17260, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is absolutely no excuse whatever for the kind of lawless behaviour that we have been seeing.\", \"from\": 17261, \"to\": 17360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexandra Humphries:Three men have already received prison sentences for their roles in the riots in Southport and Liverpool.\", \"from\": 17362, \"to\": 17487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17362, \"end\": 17371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9723915235394918, \"rank\": 0.01647448102077623, \"text\": \