used Ukraine of a large-scale provocation, following reports Ukrainian troops have made their biggest advance into Russian territory since the war began.\", \"from\": 17532, \"to\": 17729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17536, \"end\": 17553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 0.9703064601209468, \"rank\": 0.030602228367419562, \"text\": \"Russian President\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 17554, \"end\": 17568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.346970986749127e-20, \"text\": \"Vladimir Putin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 17581, \"end\": 17588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9889163291909805, \"rank\": 0.011200990678003602, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 17637, \"end\": 17646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_Air_Force\", \"score\": 0.8561701708548878, \"rank\": 0.15880211768967842, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_Air_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_Air_Force\"}, {\"begin\": 17691, \"end\": 17698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"score\": 0.9999999823710369, \"rank\": 1.6947248844273776e-08, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\"}]}, {\"se