rsk Governor Alexei Smirnov has urged residents to donate blood due to ongoing intense fighting, and he said authorities had evacuated thousands of people from the region.\", \"from\": 18849, \"to\": 19056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18898, \"end\": 18912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexei_Smirnov_(physicist)\", \"score\": 0.5937498454641255, \"rank\": 0.6477732793521878, \"text\": \"Alexei Smirnov\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexei_Smirnov_(physicist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexei_Smirnov_(physicist)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexei Smirnov:Overnight, new temporary accommodation centres with more than 2,500 places have been deployed in the region, and more than 300 people, including 121 children, have been placed in them.\", \"from\": 19058, \"to\": 19257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Declan Gooch:The fighting is near a major gas hub that serves as the only point of entry for Russian gas into the EU via Ukraine, which has continued to operate despite the war.\", \"from\": 19259, \"to\": 19436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19259, \"end\": 19265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Declan_Macey\", \"score\": 0.7916279555522331, \"rank\": 0.26239653811106556, \"text\": \"Declan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Declan_Macey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Declan_Macey\"}, {\"begin\": 19352, \"end\": 19359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.5827014864205565, \"rank\": 0.7126293629651472, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 19373, \"end\": 19375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union\", \"score\": 0.9999997131941838, \"rank\": 1.7521197326836214e-07, \"text\": \"EU\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"]